<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She puts on a sensational display daily. </p>

<p>And Amanda Holden was up to her old tricks once more on Monday as she was seen sashaying to work at Global Studios in a sensational ensemble.  </p>

<p> The hit star, 49, looked phenomenal in a green dress from high street giant Reiss as she prepared for another day of radio presenting at Heart FM. </p>

<p>Elegance personified: Amanda Holden was up to her old tricks once more on Monday as she was seen sashaying to work at Global Studios in a sensational ensemble</p>

<p>Amanda looked incredible in the stunning gown which clung to her figure to perfection, the result of gruelling hours spent in the gym.</p>

<p>She wore her blonde locks in loose waves while shielding her eyes with a pair of designer sunglasses to complete the chic look.  </p>

<p>She's been busy filling in for Simon Cowell as head judge on Britain's Got Talent, yet still found time to squeeze in some much needed relaxation time as she enjoyed a romantic getaway to Cliveden House in Berkshire this weekend.</p>

<p>Amanda put on a very loved-up display with her husband Chris Hughes during the trip before sharing a sizzling selfie of her lounging in lace while in bed.</p>

<p>Stunner: The hit star, 49, looked phenomenal in a green dress from high street giant Reiss as she prepared for another day of radio presenting at Heart FM</p>

<p>A vision: She puts on a sensational display daily</p>

<p>Happy couple: Amanda put on a very loved-up display with her husband Chris Hughes during the trip before sharing a sizzling selfie of her lounging in lace while in bed</p>

<p>She exuded glamour as she relaxed in a white dressing gown over a black lacy top while reading a book fittingly called The Mistresses Of Cliveden. </p>

<p>The blonde beauty wore her locks down for the sultry snap and added a slick of pink lipgloss as well as some smokey eyeshadow.</p>

<p>Elsewhere on the trip, Amanda and Chris appeared to enjoy the good weather as she planted a tender kiss on his cheek in a sun-soaked selfie. </p>

<p>Amanda also shared a black-and-white snap to her Instagram grid, showing her resting against a car while flaunting her toned limbs in white shorts.</p>

<p>Poser: Amanda also shared a snap of her putting on a glamorous display as she posed on a car</p>

<p>Hot stuff: She was radiant as she stepped out after a relaxing weekend </p>

<p>Taking to Instagram on Sunday, Amanda said: 'Had the best #romantic #weekend with #Chrispy in this historic and infamous place steeeeped in history.</p>

<p>'Thank you to all the staff for looking after us so well... NOT an #ad ( thanks to John on the door for humouring me by taking this pic early this morning)'</p>

<p>Cliveden house is a popular spot for celebs and has hosted an array of famous faces over the years including President Franklin D. Roosevelt and Charlie Chaplin.</p>

<p>The property, once owned by William Waldorf Astor, was also the hotel where Meghan Markle stayed the night before her wedding to Price Harry in 2018.</p>
